column5: I'm having trouble getting through to this place to get some minn kota parts.  Anyone have the inside scoop on whether they are still operating.  I know it was recently sold but I understood it was going to operate the same.  Can't get through on the phone and no reply to a message sent through their web page. Thanks,

They are still around but have moved to King st/Royce ave.  Believe the grandson is running it now.  I've seen many other posts recently from people who have dealt there.  3 Royce Ave 1 & 2 Orillia L3V 5H8 705-325-3526  Michael
I got through to them today.
I believe tyler is running the shop now and yes they are very busy and I know they were gonna be moving ...oh I see you got ahold of them....
